  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Quality Control Specialist",
  "description": "<p><p><strong>Job Title: Quality Control Specialist</strong></p><ul><li><p>Be the first line of defense, spotting and fixing quality issues in real-time.</p></li><li><p>Investigate the root cause of problems to stop them for good.</p></li><li><p>Precisely track, record, and report on production quality metrics.</p></li><li><p>Maintain critical documentation and procedures for smooth, consistent operations.</p></li><li><p>Support new projects and audits by providing accurate data and samples.</p></li><li><p>Mentor new team members on quality best practices.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>You have experience in manufacturing OR a strong, genuine curiosity about how things are made.</p></li><li><p>A natural problem-solver who connects dots to find root causes.</p></li><li><p>Hands-on, a clear communicator, and dependable under pressure.</p></li><li><p>You hold yourself to a high standard and take pride in the quality of your work.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Schedule:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Shift:</strong> Day shift (7:30 AM to 7:30 PM).</p></li><li><p><strong>Flexibility:</strong> Choose a 5-day or 6-day workweek arrangement.</p></li><li><p><strong>Support:</strong> Free shuttle bus from Choa Chu Kang and Joo Koon MRT.</p></li><li><p><strong>Team Spirit:</strong> Willing to cover occasional night shifts based on team needs.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p><strong>Competitive Pay:</strong> Basic salary of $2,500 – $2,600, plus a daily shift allowance.</p></li><li><p><strong>Strong Earnings:</strong> Monthly pay can reach $3,500+ with overtime.</p></li><li><p><strong>Financial Security:</strong> 13th-month bonus and performance bonuses (up to 2 months).</p></li><li><p><strong>Recharge:</strong> 11 days of annual leave.</p></li><li><p><strong>Grow With Us:</strong> Clear career pathways into leadership roles.</p></li></ul></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
